<includeonly>
|}</includeonly><noinclude>
Closes the `ChapterTable` frame. Invoked by SMW's `outrotemplate=`
once per `ChapterTable` call — but only when the surrounding `#ask`
yields ≥1 result. Pair with `ChapterTable/open`.

The leading newline inside `<includeonly>` puts `|}` at line start so
MediaWiki's wikitable parser recognises it as the table close.
</noinclude>
